sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as WebDriver client (Selenium)
    participant HTTP as lambda serve Server
    participant Route as Route handler
    participant Sess as WebDriverSession
    participant Loc as Locator (CSS matcher)
    participant Act as Actions (event synth)
    participant Ev as handle_event

    Client->>HTTP: POST /session/:id/element/:id/click
    HTTP->>Route: dispatch by pattern, extract params
    Route->>Sess: get_session by sessionId
    Route->>Sess: element_registry_get by elementId
    Note left of Route: for find: parse body, run locator
    Route->>Loc: traverse_views over layout view tree
    Loc->>Loc: selector_matcher_matches on DomElement
    Loc-->>Route: matched View pointer
    Route->>Act: webdriver_element_click(View)
    Act->>Act: get_element_center walks parent chain
    Act->>Ev: synthesize RdtEvent MOUSE_DOWN then UP
    Ev-->>Act: DocState dirty flags updated
    Act-->>Route: WD_SUCCESS
    Route-->>HTTP: JSON value null
    HTTP-->>Client: 200 application json
